channel.title: Moparscape is dead
channel.description:
i have been to other forums after my server status page refused to load. and every server i have written down will not work. People on these other forums are talking about how the main thing for every server crashed some time yesterday. i cannot get on, and these are not normal server failures, everything will not work.
~silver~[br][size=1]Posted on: January 13, 2007, 11:56:18 PM[/size][hr]if anyone else is having this problem, post. [br][size=1]Posted on: January 13, 2007, 11:58:05 PM[/size][hr]why the hell is no one posting...i am not some fool, the server generator crashed. wtf??
